Ibaruwa yandikiwe mama

Mama yarangije gupakira imyenda ye mu gikapu gito,

Asohoka hanze, arampobera, arambwira ati: "Mbayi ubu."

Naramwitegereje ndamubaza nti."Mama, ugiye he?"

Natangiye kurira nshaka kumukurikira ariko papa ashyira kubitugu.

Papa ati: "Nyoko agiye mu bitaro kubyara."

Igihe numvise "mwana" naretse kurira ndamureba Ndamubaza nti. "Kuki agiye gukura umwana mu bitaro?" .

Papa yicaye ku ntebe nto arambwira ati: "Nzakubwira impamvu agiye gukura umwana mu bitaro."

Namuteze namuteze yombi maze ansobanurira impamvu mama atabayariye mu rugo, nubwo ntasobanukiwe neza byose.
Papa arangije kunsobanurira, naramubajije nti: "Azakomeza kunkunda nagaruka hamwe n'undi mwana?"

Data yaranyiyegereje arambwira ati: "Tuzahora tugukunda."

Nabahise mbaza papa."Ese Nshobora kumwandikira ibaruwa akiriho?" 

Kuri uwo mugoroba, natangiye kwandikira mama ibaruwa.

Natanyuye impapuro mu gitabo cyanjye cy'imyitozo ntangira kwandika ...

"Mama, mama, papa yavuze ko wagiye kuzana undi mwana ...

... Nyamuneka ihute usubire murugo ...

... Ndashaka ko uzana umwana w'umukobwa, kugirango nzashobore gukina nawe amaze gukura ...

... Ushobora kuzana bibiri kugirango umwe abe uwanjye? ...

... Ndagutegereje hano hanze y'inzu yacu. "

Nafunze ibaruwa yanjye kugira ngo nyihe data kugira ngo ayajyanire mama. Nkibyuka bukeye bwaho, ibaruwa yari yagiye.
